No Rate Limiting on Password Reset Link

Hi team,

I found there is no rate limiting on reset password link

Description:
Rate limiting is used to control the amount of incoming and outgoing traffic to or from a network.
If the number of requests you make exceeds that limit, then an error will be triggered. 
The reasoning behind implementing rate limits is to allow for a better flow of data and to increase security by mitigating attacks such as DDoS.

